8: It looks like a show of sorts.
12:
You thought you could deceive THE 
Naska Etranger? Tsk, tsk... That was 
your first mistake, my friend!
14:
Not to mention your sleight of hand 
was WAY too sloppy. What is this, 
amateur hour?
19:
Don't tell me you're about to tuck tail 
and run—the REAL game's only just 
begun!
29:
If you TRULY fancy yourself a gambler, 
you won't run, will you? Or are you too 
chicken to play without your lousy 
cheats?
37: Hmm... Let's see. You there! Catch!
44:
Yup! If the goddess is on top, that's 
heads. If it's a number, that's tails.
47:
That's all there is to it!
So... heads or tails?
50:
Are you nuts, lady?! There's no 
strategy involved here whatsoever—
it's 100 percent luck!
52:
EXACTLY. That's what makes it all so 
THRILLING, right?
54:
I think it's gonna be tails, by the way. I'll 
let you choose first though. Well? 
What's it gonna be?
56:
I'll even go all in with my money too! 
The bigger the stakes, the greater the 
thrill!
58: You're goin' all in... on a fifty-fifty?!
59:
You must be out of your mind if you 
think I'd participate in your crazy 
games!
64:
That's fine—it's no fun unless both of 
us are into it, you know what I mean?
67:
Aww, seriously? Boo that man! 
Booooo!
70:
Now, now, everyone.
And what was the verdict, by the way?
81:
Say, you folks wanna grab some 
lunch? Us otherworlders gotta stick 
together, right?
89: Why did things end up like this?
92: It's all thanks to lady luck, of course!
96:
I'm impressed. How did you figure we 
were from a different world?
99:
Call it a hunch. You guys just had 
a different vibe, you know?
101:
But I seriously can't believe this rabbit 
used to be some kinda hero! And your 
whole journey sounds like it's been full 
of thrills so far!
110:
Of course! I mean, this makes things 
way more fun, doesn't it?
112:
Say... Do you think I could join you 
guys on your journey too?
118: You're more than welcome to join us.
126:
You sure you don't need some time to 
think about it?
128:
Nope. Lady Luck hasn't let me down so 
far!
130:
And you can count on me—Naska 
Etranger's a safe bet every time!
